Text:
It is time.
To the north and east!

Halt! It is too quiet...
Even the crickets do not sing...

Drop your weapons and we'll
let your women live...with us!

'Tis fortunate they were
drunk. Alcohol will gift a man
bravery...but always for a price.

We'll be taking these...
and these...and also these.

Hahaha! Tonight we dine
as champions of the steppe!

The steppe is no
place for the weak!

The bandits will tell others
of this battle, and they will
be drawn to the promise of
blood and plunder. We move!

There! A lone warrior...and
a mammoth!

Then she will not survive.
That is the way of the steppe.
No! We cannot just leave her!

The steppe is full of enemies.
This is why we must embrace
newfound friends.
There is little life left in her.

She was a fool to
walk the steppe alone.

That's no reason to leave
her to die, Anarba!

We shall make camp here
and decide as a tribe how
we are to proceed.

I will see to the
stranger's wounds.

Won't eat, you say?
That is odd...

It might be they
sense something amiss.

You stay here while I see
if I cannot discover the
reason for their disquiet.

That horse... It doesn't
appear to be one of ours.

You look hungry. Come with
me. Altani will see you fed
and watered.

I have you and your tribe
to thank for that.

My apologies. I was just so─
I am Gurbesu of the Goro.

My tribe's food tents were
destroyed in a Matanga raid.

I went hunting to replenish
our supplies and in my
desperation─

If you had not intervened...
My life, I owe to your
people.

What of the rest
of your tribe?

I do not know. We lost many
in the raid, and if the Matanga
attacked again while I was
hunting...

Blood to earth!
Blood to earth!

They were no match
for our courage.

The Matanga...
They were here for me.

I am the cause
of this destruction.

Nonsense! You shared our
water, our fire. You stood
at our side in battle.

What will you do now,
Gurbesu of the Goro?
The only thing I can─search for my tribe.
Then we will search with you.

You are one of us now, and
we would not allow a sister
to walk the steppe alone.
I... I don't know what to say...

Then say nothing.
It is already decided.

We ride, my people!
But keep your weapons
at the ready! All eyes ahead!

The Matanga have returned...
and this time in numbers.

Something is wrong. That was
too organized for a retreat...

Then let us rest
while we can.

Gurbesu. You say that
beyond lies the location
of your tribe's last camp?

Yes, Khan. While I expect it
to be abandoned, perhaps
we will find some clue as
to which direction they fled.
We should be nearing it now.

It appears your tribe did not
leave...nor did the Matanga!

Blood to earth!
Blood to earth!

Death come, Au Ra!
Death come!

My brothers! My sisters!
You are safe!

As are you and Bayan.
This is good.
But you do not come alone.

Why would the Dataq lift
their spears for the Goro?

We would lift them for
Gurbesu, so we would
lift them for you.

Death to Au Ra!
Death to trunkless!

Blood to earth!
Blood to earth!

There is no Dataq and no
Goro. Only sisters and
brothers of the steppe!

Anjana come!
Give blood to earth!

They break! Now the
slaughter begins!

Anarba! Is it not enough
that the day is ours?

Khan is right, Anarba. No
more blood need be spilled
this day.

Let us see to the wounded
then leave this cursed place.

Brothers and sisters of the
Dataq, we are forever in
your debt.

The song of your tribe's
bravery will be sung at
our fires for generations
to come.

As they will at ours,
brave Goro. Until we
meet again.

Dataq! To your mounts.
We ride!

The more mercy you show, the less you'll receive from me!
Now, BEGIN!

Guerrilla tactics, shield
walls─neither'll save my
men from the cannons of
an imperial reaper.

No... What they need is
something unpredictable.
Something volatile...

There is only one rule on
the front lines: don't break.
Break and you're dea─

A parry that slow
will be your last!
How long do we have to wait?

They promise us a mock
battle, but give us lectures.

Hahaha! I haven't been so
frightened for my life since
I was a recruit!

Do you think they've
had enough?

Enough? When I was their
age I broke my fast on
heroes of the realm!

But that doesn't mean I'm
letting them off easy!

Fools! Beaten by your
own meaten!

That is why always you
are hungering!

How did they
get behind us!?

The village is
not much further!

Thank you, traveler. My
tribe will see me safe now.
There is nowhere to run, boy!

Your tribe will not have
you back now!
One of us! One of us!

Were you going to call
in reinforcements?

<sigh> Another night in
the stables, I reckon.

Neutralize the enemy's capacity to heal its wounded.
Standard battle tactics.
And then there was one─one with the strength of ten!
I wasn't in best form today...
You needn't have pulled your punches...but this act of clemence is certain to cheer the men's spirits. <wink>

Not all our men are as green
as the recruits!

If you underestimated us,
perhaps the Empire will, too!
Much was to be had from the day's exercises.
May they see us─may they see Eorzea to victory!
My instruments are picking something up!

It was an honor to exchange
blows with you this day.

Of course, emerging victorious
didn't hurt, either. Gah hah hah!

Time to check the nets
I laid last night.

Flying sharks!? This far
from the Tide!?

My nets torn and my catch
devoured! What am I to do!?

Now I'll have to find a new
place farther up river!

The waters no longer boil.
The sharks have returned
to the Tide.

Now to see if there is aught
remaining of my ne─

Hells take me! It's a...a...
giant weasel!

What have I done
to deserve this!?
It is! The weasel is dead!

Wait... Flying sharks and giant
weasels? My wife is never
going to believe me!
I need to catch some fish...now!

How am I going to explain
this to my wife? I'm doomed...

What are we going to do?
What are we going to do!?

Is this enough? I suppose it's
enough... But what if it's not
enough? What if old nan dies
because we didn't have that
one last seedling!

Thank the stars
we will not starve!

We're doomed... The Empire
will take what little we have
and leave us to starve!

Four here... Six there...
They're everywhere!

If all these eggs
were to hatch...

You have already brought
me so many, I couldn't think
of asking you to bring more...
unless you wanted to, that is.

The village thanks you...
as does my belly!

I must warn
the other villagers...

It can't be...!
It was just a story!

This is the place
the villagers spoke of.

From here emerges the evil
spirit that haunts their fields.
It is here I will find my quarry!

Shall I wait,
or shall I attack?

Can you feel it?
The creature approaches!

What foul plot requires
this many servants!?

I will not be
defeated so easily!
Come! I do not fear death!

I may have
failed the village...

But this land has not seen
the last of Senban Oneblade!

The onmyoji's henchmen will
trouble the villagers no longer.

Yet I fear his work
is far from complete.

He plots something most
treacherous, and I will not
rest until he has been silenced!

A plump pack you have
there traveler! Oh, so plump!

Don't eat me! I'm fugu!
Aaaaaack!

Gouge herhis eyes!
Cut out herhis tongue!

None who bear witness
shall be suffered to live!

You have not seen
the last of us, meddler!

What funny hats...
Maybe they'll let me have one.

Gaei out battling
injustice again, eh?

Looks as if both
sides are Lupin.

You know how Gaei gets
about trading blows with
his brothers.

You're free to do what you
please, my friend. I'll stay here.
Argh! That smarts...! What are these... Arrows?

Uh... We can still discuss
this like civil wolves!

We've enough to worry about
here without those shellbacks.

Let this one live, and another
hundred will be on the shores
by new moon.

Victory is sweetest when
won with a straight heart!

None can withstand the
might of Yojimbo! Hahahah!
You have a feel for the blade.

They won't make
me one of them!
We came for the treasure! Yes, yes! Where is it?
It is mine! Everything here─it is all mine!
To go left or to go right? That is the question...
Show no mercy to any who stand in our way!
You want to fight? Yes, yes! Well, it is a fight you will get!
Aaargh! SheHe got me─right in the gut!
The best fighters know when to stay and when to flee! Ghahaha! You shan't catch me!

I'm never leaving
my bed again!

Was it truly Tsurubebi...
or something else...?

No. Don't tell me.
I don't want to know.

I'm never leaving
my bed again!

Those are mine!
Mine! Mine! Mine!
Hit him in the head! The head!

Those are mine!
Mine! Mine! Mine!

Right to the whiskers!
The whiskers!
Pick the pack! Pick the pack!

Keep your plump pack!
Keep it! Keep it!

Might I suggest a strategic,
yet not at all shameful retreat?

They'll think twice before
coming back...won't they?

Kindest of kindly strangers!
Mimiroon is most grateful
for such kind kindness!

You will protect me, then?
Twelve be praised!

Rats as those deserve
no mercy! Not a damn whit!

Spoken like a
true fellow warrior!
My life is in your hands!
I have herhim! I have herhim!
My legs are about to give out.
Maybe I should have brought my sword...
I cannot carry on much longer...
So this is the Isle of Endless Summer. Beautiful.
Oh me, oh my, look at all these lovely little things out today. And they're all just my type.
What was that? I could have sworn I heard something.
Hey, ladies! Care to come have a romp with me?
Don't be shy, now. There's no use running away!
A talking octopus!? Is this some new voidsent!?
Ugh, all those muscles. You're not my type!
I may be just an octopus, but I'll not lose to the likes of you!
This is not looking good... Oh no, I forgot to call Master Typhon.
I yield, I yield! I just wanted...to enjoy the faire...like everyone else.
I find that hard to believe.
I promise I'll be good. I swear!
Do you? Step out of line again, and you won't get off so easy.
Gwee-hee-hee. I promise, I promise. An octopus always keeps his word.
Mwa ha ha! Just my type!
I can't be bothered with this anymore!
Gwee-hee-hee! Where are all the laaadies!?
The big ones are biting! Need any bait?
Could you stand to part with one of those?
Trying to make off without paying? Get back here, you bastard!
You looking to get yourself hurt?
Bah, damned faire chaperones. Come on!
I'm leaving this fight to you!
Go back to your damn faire!
These bastards are strong... Retreat! Retreat!
Serves you right for not minding your business. Come on, after that fisherman!
Ugh... It's no use. We have to fall back.
All that's left is to deliver these fish.
Snippers! Why did it have to be snippers!?
Thanks. You saved me, and my fish.
No! My fish... My beautiful fish...
Gods be good... Look at all this rubbish!
Thank you! You've made the beach beautiful again!
It's no good. There's still too much rubbish. We may need more hands.
Bring me your rubbish! Every last bit you can find!
Gather your rubbish! I'll collect it!
Thanks for the help. I think our work here is done.
If you still have rubbish, I'll take it off your hands!
A promisingplain Treasure is discovered upon defeating BNpcName!
You still wish to fight? My sword is only too happy to oblige!
The world has no place for such wretches.
Your claim to life is forfeit!
Death is too light a punishment for your ilk!

O hallowed moon,
shine you the iron path!

O hallowed moon,
take fire and scorch my foes!

Blazing path,
lead me to iron rule!

From on high I descend,
the iron path to walk!

From on high I descend,
the hallowed moon to call!

Fleeting light!
Amid a rain of stars,
exalt you the red moon!

Fleeting light!
'Neath the red moon,
scorch you the earth!

From on high I descend,
the moon and stars to bring!

From hallowed moon I descend,
a rain of stars to bring!

Unbending iron,
take fire and descend!

Unbending iron,
descend with fiery edge!

From hallowed moon I descend,
upon burning earth to tread!

From hallowed moon I bare iron,
in my descent to wield!
I smell woodsmoke. There was a battle here.
No wonder there's a desert above. All the water's down here!
That's not Dalmascan he's speaking. Could it be High Ivalician?
You understood him...? Right! The Echo!
You ain't supposed to be here!
Grab all you can carry, brothers!
We got no choice but to kill 'em!

Mother. Father.
I come to you now...

Theodoric...
The Hells burn for you...

Now! While Fordola's
taking the brunt of it...
I'll not lose to the likes of this...

Walked into a trap,
have we?
It's like a gold mine...without the mine!
I's never before seen so much riches.
Three ways, brothers. Just as we agreed upon.
The pounding takes place just over yonder.
Please,  , we must have that mochi!
Take care to avoid the cyclops's mallet.
There can be no celebration without that mochi.
Yes, that should more than suffice. Well done, my friend!
Our mochi... What will become of the festival now?
What say ye just let us be, eh?
Only death will you find here! Only death!
The Red will rue this day!
May the blessings of the kami grant you strength.
I will rend you limb from limb!

Where did she─?
Stay on your guard!
May the kami keep you safe.

The Red will think twice
before challenging us again.
The kami's blessing will protect you.

Waters to strip
flesh from bone!

Waters to burst
and drag below!

Don't worry Azami.
I won't let them hurt you.

You refuse?
Then slake the land's thirst with a storm of blood!
Yes, hold your heads high... My gales will sever them before long.
Defy me not, for I am your lord! I am your god! I am Pazuzu!
I witness this windswept land, and claim it my own.
This land, and the rabble who walk upon it!
Lay down your arms and rejoice before your lord!
Get away from her, you bitch!
Now, now. Be a good meal and lie still.

Is this...my blood? Why is it not your blood!
Your blood, your bloodyourbloodyourBLOOOOOOD!
My, what a tantalizingly pure soul you have!
And you've come all this way to offer it to me.
I can hardly wait...so I shan't. Let the feast begin!
Your bravery will not be forgotten.

I hate fighting so I
better let you pass!

I have more lives
than I do arms!
Have no fear! The power of love is on our side!
Ignore me, these creatures do. But why...?

Squawk! Squawk! How is this possible!?
Strongly resembles the Ixal, this feathered one does.
Those creatures... Mistake me for this, I fear.

You go on ahead,  .
I'll, uh...wait here.

! Thank the Twelve you're okay.
What say we get out of here, eh?
Why mussst you be ssso blind?
Time for me to prove myssself!
It'll all be for nothing if you get yourself killed!
Don't blame me if you wind up dead!
You've bitten off more than you can chew!

Behold the strength of a nunh!
Future nunh, anyway...
It'll take more than that to stop me!
I'd rather be reading a book...
Does anyone fancy taking a break?

Look upon me!
Behold the divine!
You turn your back on terror?
You dare lock eyes with fear?

A portrayal of fire!
Your world in flames!

A portrayal of wind!
A shrieking gale!

A portrayal of water!
All is drowned!

A portrayal of earth!
The ground shall shudder!

Whither goes the wind,
Her dance unseen by thee?♪

Bearing seeds afar,
Breeze knows no boundary.♪

To those blessed with life,
Her boon is but to be.♪

I am Siegfried, the greatest
swordsman in all the world!

You should have fled!
Now feel my wrath!
Alright, everyone. Are you ready for some fun?
I hope you have your red lights ready. Tee hee hee.
Thank you all so much for coming.
Let's make this a Little Ladies' Day to remember, with plenty of yellow lights, if you please.
Quite a large crowd today, isn't it girls?
Should make for quite the sight with all of their blue lights, am I right?

That's all for now.
But we'll be back!
You were all fantastic. Thank you!
I can hardly wait for the next show.

Ugh, all those muscles.
You're not my type!

One last test...
This should help
wrap things up.
I will cassst your ashes to the wind!
Good day, fine sirs, how may I be of service?

The beach is clear.
Just the ones here now!

Just a puff or two
before we go on!
I'll grind you under my heel!

Widow of Sashihai...
Witch of Doma!

Your fall from grace is
long overdue, savage!

Artful wiles won't
save you now!

Worthless, I say.
Might as well be dead!

Just the sight of
your face sickens me!
I should have been the one!

Asahi...
You, more than any other...
How did it come to this?
Keep as still as you can!

Desertion is punishable
by death! My death!
I hope I live to regret this...
Why did shehe have to run!?
I see you, and the darkness that awaits...
Very well. Enough of this guise. I shall suffer thee no longer!
Thou shalt repent, and kneel before me!
A blizzard of aether? What a peculiar land.
Or should I say battlefield? For that I am here can only mean...
...you are a foe worthy of testing!
No going b-b-back now, I suppose?
You think we're high enough yet?
Well, aren't those simply appalling, kupo!
The brave do not fear the grave.
You're looking a bit worse for wear!
Hm. You have some measure of strength, at least.
A pity you will soon be but rime on my blades!

This should cut you
down to size!

Uh-oh! Someone just
woke the dragon...

Not the strongest of swords,
but it should suffice.

Behold, the sword art
of legend─Zanmato!

The seas part for
Gilgamesh alone!

And now for something
truly shocking!

Reevaluating combat efficacy.
Initiating self-destruct mechanism...
The training will soon commence. Stand by until all participants are present.
Steel yourselves! The Calamity is upon us!
First, make haste for the Gate of Nald! The Garleans have broken through!
Join your strength and meet the enemy as one!
What's the matter? Is that the best you can do?
Remember what it is you are fighting to protect!
Hurry to the aetheryte plaza, and keep your wits about you! A colossal fiend has appeared!
That concludes the training! Well fought, one and all!
The final foe comes! Vanquish the enormous voidsent and see Ul'dah saved!
This is for your own good!
Let me help, kupo! A little moogle magic for one!
Whoever the lucky person is─make it count, kupo!

Entries for the special limited-time event are now closed.
We look forward to your participation in events to come!
You've come for treasure, yes? Then treasure you shall have!
To the Gate of the Sultana! Dread fiends and voidsent have appeared!
Make for the aetheryte plaza! A massive morbol is on a rampage!
Those who wish to continue fighting, gather to me. The next session will soon commence.
Are there no heroes here to bare their blades against me?
Do you all cling to your little lives so?
I will help you find freedom in a fight to the death!
You are not yet ash? Impressive.
Worthy warriors all, I see. No doubt you have dealt many a glorious death.
I honor you with this battlefield─here shall our souls burn bright!
Our land lives, its laughter a fiery red.♪
A burning being, a blaze at its heart.♪
Fan its flames to find us there alight.♪

Irrational behavior observed.
Inefficient energy expenditure.
I'm coming, coming, coming for you...
Why, why, why won't you play with me!?

We shall retrieve
our rightful mochi yet!

Excellent. These pieces
may be safely delivered.
What slavering mortals dare profane my lands?
By the authority of the abyssal court I command thee, darkness, rise!
You will learn your place, even as you breathe your last...
Pshhh... Shkohhh... Interfering uplanders come even to farlands?
Pshhh... Shkohhh... Lamebrix crush uplanders this time for sure!
Pssshkoh... Lamebrix has new toys for funplaying! Spent much jinglyshine!
This oughta be the right place.
